rows.label: qst200211_msg0001
rows.name:
Thank friends for saving!
Jaruru very grateful!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0002
rows.name:
Think nothing of it!
I just did what any hero would do.

rows.label: qst200211_msg0003
rows.name:
What were you doing in a dangerous
place like this anyway?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0006
rows.name: What kind of goods do you sell?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0007
rows.name:
Go on, let's have a look. We might
be able to give you some custom!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0008
rows.name:
Urk... J-Jaruru not have any
wares right now.

rows.label: qst200211_msg0009
rows.name:
What? You're a traveling merchant
with nothing to sell?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0010
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh!
Nasty monsters stole all of wares!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0011
rows.name:
They did what?!
Well, that's not good at all!

rows.label: qst200211_msg0012
rows.name:
The monsters we just beat up didn't
seem to be carrying anything, though...

rows.label: qst200211_msg0014
rows.name:
Is it just me, or is this Nopon
acting reeeeeally suspicious?

rows.label: qst200211_msg0015
rows.name:
Yes, I get the feeling he may be
hiding something. Let's see if we
can't get it out of him.
